Release for the eMedication test event, taking place in March 2021.
Main changes:
- added original representation as requirement for all eMed documents
- changed document type according to current annex 3 (old types were deprecated)
- added value set UnitOfPresentation to set the dosequantity
- issues solved, see below
- issues of ch-pharm solved, release of ch-pharm 0.97
There have been changes to the following 10 issues since the last intermediate version or release.
